nc.com.analyzer

Class Analyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • nc.com.analyzer.Analyzer

  • public class Analyzer
extends java.lang.Object
    A Analyzer provides information about sorts by using Reflections. This class contains a analyze() that collects data in a list of statistics using reflections.
    See Also:
